    "body": "I also like the current names. In particular I think `balanceOfAt` does a good job at showing it's the same thing as `balanceOf`, _at_ a particular snapshot. Getting something _from_ a snapshot looks strange, snapshots don't actually store anything themselves.\r\n\r\nRegarding the 0-indexing, ids are just identifiers: they should not be expected to be sequential.",
